text: A state bird is the insignia of a nation or a state (sub-national entity). For lists of these animals, see: * List of national birds, national birds on country level * List of Australian bird emblems, for the Australian states * List of Brazilian state birds, for the Brazilian states * List of Indian state birds, for the Indian states * List of U.S. state birds, for the U.S. states == See also == * List of national animals, for a list of other animals per country * List of animals representing first-level administrative country subdivisions, for a list of animals on the sub-country level Category:Symbols of country subdivisions
title: State bird
